     <!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0;"}-->
      ^detail-heading^ #### Description
      ^detail-body^ Statically typed superset of JavaScript used for large-scale web applications, tooling, and shared platform packages.
      ^detail-heading^ #### Notes
      ^detail-body^ Primary application language. Uses strict mode throughout with explicit types at API boundaries. Comfortable with both frontend and Node.js contexts.

    <!--hvy:expandable:content {}-->

